VShashank started with Bhairavi ata tala varnam. Then he went forSripathi Neepadachintanelekain Nagaswaravali of Thyagaraja, with raga essay andswarakalpanadelightfully presented.Ninne Namminanuof Vasudevachar in Simhendra Madhyamam in Misrachapu ragam along withneravuandswarakalpanawas the main show piece of the concert.Enta Muddo, Enta Sogasowas dominated by aswaraprastharahe did in a raga chain comprising of almost a dozen ragas, displaying wonderful control. Ragas Behag, Bhoopalam, Mohana, Hamsadhwani, Kapi, Desh, Abheri, Hindolam, Hamsanadi and few others figured.  Then he played a Bhajan in Yamuna Kalyani and ended his show withVisweswar Darshan Karoin Sindhubahairavi. Satish Kumar and Ramanamurthy&#8217;stani avartanamwas by itself an experience to listen too, as they played withbhava.
